KG name: GovWILD - Government Web Integration for Linked Data
Description: GovWILD integrates Open Government Data about politicians- parties- government agencies- funds- companies- and industrial leaders into a clean and consistent data set. This interlinked data is visualized on a Web interface to be explored by citizens and is available for download and further analysis. It can be used to uncover hidden connections between individuals in government and industry- to aggregate financial data- and to deep-dive into the network of politics and industry.
